OL,3,CGovernment warned it rushed decision
OL,4,Cto scrap winter fuel payments
OL,6,FLabour's winter fuel payment cut has
OL,7,Fbeen criticised as 'rushed' by a House
OL,8,Fof Lords committee, as ITV News Deputy
OL,9,FPolitical Editor Anushka Asthana
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FMembers of the House of Lords whose
OL,13,Fjob it is to scrutinise legislation
OL,14,Fhave warned that the government has
OL,15,Funnecessarily rushed through its
OL,16,Fdecision to scrap winter fuel
OL,17,Fpayments, leaving too little time for
OL,18,Fits impact to be properly considered.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
