OL,3,CGovernment warned it rushed decision
OL,4,Cto scrap winter fuel payments
OL,6,FThe warning also makes clear that the
OL,7,Fchanges could cause "potential
OL,8,Finequalities" between low income
OL,9,Fpensioners, but adds, "it is not clear
OL,10,Fwhether DWP (the Department for Work
OL,11,Fand Pensions)) has assessed this risk".
OL,13,FThe warning from a committee that
OL,14,Fincludes peers from a number of
OL,15,Fparties, such as Labour, comes as Sir
OL,16,FKeir Starmer faces increased pressure
OL,17,Fover his decision to means test the
OL,18,Funiversal benefit.
