OL,3,CGovernment warned it rushed decision
OL,4,Cto scrap winter fuel payments
OL,6,FAhead of a binding vote on the
OL,7,Fdecision on Tuesday, there is unease
OL,8,Fon the prime minister's backbenches,
OL,9,Fwith 12 Labour MPs signing an early
OL,10,Fday motion calling for the policy to
OL,11,Fbe delayed.
OL,13,FThe motion was laid by the Labour MP
OL,14,Ffor Poole - Neil Duncan-Jordan.
OL,15,FAnother Labour MP, Lee Barron, has
OL,16,Fwritten to Chancellor Rachel Reeves to
OL,17,Fsay his "main concern is ensuring that
OL,18,Fno pensioner is at risk of falling
OL,19,Fthrough the gaps".
