OL,3,CGovernment warned it rushed decision
OL,4,Cto scrap winter fuel payments
OL,6,FThere are a number of Cabinet members
OL,7,Fwho have privately raised concerns,
OL,8,Fwhile former shadow chancellor Ed
OL,9,FBalls has spoken out, saying the
OL,10,Fgovernment needs "an escape route"
OL,11,Ffrom the policy.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, there are also concerns
OL,14,Fabout how much money the change will
OL,15,Factually save.
OL,17,FThe policy is to limit winter fuel
OL,18,Fpayments to those who already receive
OL,19,Fpension credit.
