OL,3,CGovernment warned it rushed decision
OL,4,Cto scrap winter fuel payments
OL,6,FOnly 63% of those who qualify access
OL,7,Fthe benefit, leading to fears that
OL,8,Falmost one million poor pensioners -
OL,9,Fwho qualify for pension credit but do
OL,10,Fnot access it - could now be pushed
OL,11,Finto hardship as they lose their
OL,12,Fwinter fuel payment.
OL,14,FThat is why the government is urging
OL,15,Fpeople take up pension credit - and
OL,16,Fhas assumed that 5% more will do so in
OL,17,Fits calculation of the overall savings
OL,18,Ffrom the policy (#1.3 billion and then
OL,19,F#1.5 billion per year).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
