OL,3,CGovernment warned it rushed decision
OL,4,Cto scrap winter fuel payments
OL,6,FBut if they were more successful, and
OL,7,Fpushed up pension credit take-up to
OL,8,F100%, the Institute for Fiscal Studies
OL,9,F(IFS) tell me that would cost over #2
OL,10,Fbillion - more than the savings from
OL,11,Fmeans testing winter fuel payments.
OL,13,FCarl Emmerson, IFS deputy director,
OL,14,Ftold : "The rationale behind choosing
OL,15,Fto target winter fuel payments at the
OL,16,Fpoorest pensioners, rather than having
OL,17,Fa universal payment, is clear.
