OL,6,F"It means that the cost for the
OL,7,Ftaxpayer is reduced. And it is
OL,8,Fimportant to remember that on average
OL,9,Fpensioner incomes are no longer below
OL,10,Fthat of the population as a whole.
OL,12,F"But the challenge is then how to get
OL,13,Fwinter fuel payments successfully to
OL,14,Fpoorer pensioners."
OL,16,FHe argued that while targeting pension
OL,17,Fcredit claimants is the obvious and
OL,18,Fstraightforward way to do this, there
OL,19,Fare an estimated 880,000 low income
OL,20,Fpensioner households who are entitled
OL,21,Fto pension credit but don't claim it.
